Do you want to control your expenses and be always aware of how much money you have spent and obtained over the past day, week, month or even year? This program will be the best financial assistant for you in this regard.

You will always be informed of your financial possibilities. The app will show you, where you can save money and where you can spend more than usual. It is much easier to do this by using categories (food, clothes, car), accounts (cash, bank card, deposit), currencies (dollars, euros, pounds) and transfers (from one account to another).

Your details will be securely saved. Syncing with the cloud will save your data, even if the device fails to function. You can set the app logon password, just in case your device is used by others, so you can stop worrying about your data confidentiality.

You can easily use the application and you will be able to quickly add new recordings of expenses. The program requires a minimum of time for keeping records; it is easy enough for novices, while it provides rich functionality and a lot of settings for experienced users.

One base on different devices. Thanks to the syncing with the cloud, the whole family can use the application. Your phone will inform you of any change in the database with a notification. You can log in to the app using other devices or via WEB-interface (browser), following the link “http://walletsapp.com”.

Forget about past problems of unknown losses and counting money for a long time. Now you have a reliable program that will help you:
- Reduce your expenses;
- Calculate the total capital in different currencies;
- Save your family budget;
- Assess your financial possibilities;

As our ancestors used to say, money likes to be counted! Therefore, a personal banking system allows you to safely manage any money transactions, look through charts and reports, and sort your incomings and expenses according to different categories. Download the mobile application and do not lose sight of any financial transaction.

System capabilities:
- Addition of accounts (including multicurrency), categories (and subcategories);
- Addition of transactions and remittances (in the same or different currencies);
- View of the current exchange rates used in the application;
- Syncing with the cloud and with different devices;
- App logon password;
- View of the current funds in the same currency;
- Graphical reports according to the categories, accounts and currencies;
- Daily, weekly, monthly and annual reports on the incomings and expenses;
- Graphic report on the size of the capital in different currencies for a selected period;
- Log in to the application database via a browser (WEB-version), following the link http://walletsapp.com.

Differences from the free version:
- No advertising;

Create your own financial history and always keep up with the flow of your own cash!

Convenient worksheet-like comparison table of any three currencies.

Main features: 
- Fast currency exchange rate updating (from Central Bank of Russia or EU or bloomberg.com or National Bank of Ukraine);
- Possibility of entering an exchange rate adjustment factor;
- Manual exchange rate editing;
- Fast switching between different currencies;
- Arbitrary increment for a chosen currency in a comparison table;
- Arbitrary precision level for each currency in a comparison table;
- English or Russian interface depending on the phone default language settings...

How often when traveling abroad you asked yourself looking at the price tags - how much is that in my national currency (or in some other currency, say dollars or euro)? Though sometimes this question could be asked even if you shopping locally but want to know what the price will be in different currency.

And now with the help of this app the answers for those questions are on the tips of your fingers (verbatim). Simple and convenient!

This simple tool is a must for everyone who deals with prices in different currencies to save money or to satisfy curiosity:). With the touch of one finger to see the exchange rates of the three countries in the most readable form. You can quickly scroll through the table to the right you see the parity of currencies of various countries. For example, in travel, in most cases, we need exactly three currency - the currency of your home country, the currency of the host country, and the dollar (or euro). 
To work in places where there is no Internet or no desire to pay for roaming, the program has the ability to set currency rates manually. 
The main advantage of this program - very easy to use interface in the style of the multiplication tables. 

Data on exchange rates, the program loads directly from the web-site of the Central Bank of the EU or Russia or bloomberg.com, and does not use any intermediate server. The developer is not responsible for the accuracy of these data as well as for any consequences of using this information.

First: spending less does not mean living better.
Second: to make more money, you need to spend more.
Third: the first two rules work only if you know what you are paying for.  
In this store you will easily discover dozens of applications for managing personal finance, and all of them will help you be economical, but tr.en.d beyond that will help you be successful. 

The unique tr.en.d accounting system allows you to:
• focus not on the expenses themselves, but on the benefits they bring;
• learn how expenses affect your life;
• estimate how much a day of your life costs and what the money is spent on: urgent needs, pleasure or development;
• control your standard of living and analyze its profile;
and as a result: know yourself and your life better, understand your strengths and move on.

In addition, tr.en.d is a handy application for personal finance accounting.
• Enter financial records at any date of the past and the future without restrictions.
• Open accounts in different currencies.
• The double budgeting will allow for both long-term trends, and current plans.
• Group records into projects and monitor the finances in a separate area.
• With an easy set-up, create regular payments of two different types: periodic and ongoing.

The application forms a convenient summary for any period: the illustrative graphs and diagrams will help you in analyzing your finances.

Besides, in tr.en.d you will find: 
• The list of categories and subcategories of arbitrary nesting;
• Live currency exchange rates;
• Locking the application with a PIN code and a password;
• Export of data on the records in csv, xml, html formats;
• Synchronization between devices by means of iCloud (this feature is introduced at the beta testing level).

Focus on benefits!

Our Any Currency Converter is your easiest way to get the live exchange rates for any world currency. Our app provides an opportunity to convert any currency and to compare it to your local one or to the currency you are interested in. It is a real must-have not only for businesses that are closely connected with the currencies market, but for everyone who would like to convert prices on-the-go when abroad or while online-shopping. 

Features:
- Availability of any world currency to convert, including cryptocurrencies;
- Automatic local currency detection;
- Easy-to-use interface;
- Full Dark Mode support;
- Interactive map showing all the ATMs and banks nearby;
- Several currencies at once on the main screen with an opportunity for simultaneous conversion;
- Integrated currency calculator;
- Customizable currencies list;
- On-the-go exchange rates comparison using the widget in a Curtain mode on your iPhone and currency conversion on your Apple Watch;
- Compatibility with iPhone, Apple Watch and iPad;
- Technical requirements: iOS 9+ or iPadOS, Watch OS 2.0+

We are constantly working hard on making the currency converter app better and more useful for you. We need your constant support to get going. Please feel free to email us for any queries/suggestions/problems or if you just want to say hi. We'd love to hear from you. Do not forget to rate us if you like.

Binance Smart Chain Explorer is an app that allows you to track BEP-20 transactions of public addresses easily, on iPhone, iPad and Mac.

It features:
- Multiple accounts functionality;
- Get real-time notifications for transactions executed by any wallet address (available with monthly/yearly subscription);
- Periodic notifications! Get notifications for new transactions for up to 5 accounts! Please note that the notifications are not real-time yet;
- Add any address coin or transaction hash to favorites to keep them better organized;
- Add groups to organize addresses and expand or collapse them as you like.  Groups and their collapsed state are synchronized on all your devices via iCloud;
- You can filter the list to see the transactions you want;
- Transactions can be sorted by various options;
- View coin details;
- View transactions of any address without leaving the app and also add them to the saved account lists if you want;
- Possibility to add alias to every address for a better visibility;
- Added accounts are now automatically synchronised via iCloud;
- Tapping on one coin, tx or other addresses will redirect you to PancakeSwap/BSC Scan;
- Light mode and Dark mode support;
- Accessibility support. We have optimized the apps for VoiceOver and for Dynamic Font Size.
- Handoff support. Continue what you started viewing or editing on your other devices.

If you do have questions or for feedback you can contact us at support@crapps.io anytime.

Thanks for using our app!

